-- Swiss Stocks Pare Losses; SMI Is Little Changed as ABB Shares Advance
-- Sarah Jones
-- 2010-07-22T07:40:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/swiss-stocks-pare-losses-smi-is-little-changed-as-abb-shares-advance.html

          
          
             Swiss stocks pared losses, as shares
of ABB Ltd. climbed.  
 The benchmark Swiss Market Index slid 0.1 percent to
6,129.17 at 9:38 a.m. in Zurich after earlier falling as much as
0.5 percent  
 ABB climbed 1.9 percent to 20.03 francs after the company
forecast a recovery in demand in the power business. Credit
Suisse Group AG and Syngenta AG paced declining shares after the
companies reported earnings.  
          
          


  


        